&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Children&#39;s Nurse - 12 month FTC to cover maternity leave.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Band 6- £30,401 - £37,267 + HCAS £4560 - £4743&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a Paediatric Nurse with community or learning disability nursing experience who is considering a new job for 2021?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bromley Healthcare Integrated Children’s Community Nursing Team may be the team for you. This team of nurses and health care assistants currently provide services within the child’s home, in schools and at clinics for children in accordance with our service specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hours are 0800 until 2000 dependant on needs Monday to Friday and 0900 until 1400 on Saturday and Sunday to meet the needs of the community and also provide 24 hour on call care for children at end of life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will work with other team members to provide family centred nursing care, support and advice that is responsive, evidence based and high quality to meet our contractual obligations. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This is an exciting time to join our service as the changes within the NHS are impacting positively on the development and expansion of the children’s community nursing team. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Part time hours would be considered at a minimum of 22.5hrs/week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
